subject: I Have No Life
text:
Open 2 full boxes of tablets, 
switch off the lights
and lock the door, 
take 2 handfulls
and swallow, 
i wait to die, 
on the floor i lie, 
It waz the only way to out
I had no life
no i forget everything
i leave all my troubles behind, 
a whole new world i find, 
here, i have a life!
